# uritemplate

Generate and parse Uri templates based on RFC 6570. 

## Usage

- uribuilder: TBD
- uriparser: TBD
     	    
## Todo

- PCTs in literals 
- handle missing } in templates
- handle prefix together with explode
- uriparser
    (let [example-parser (uri-parser "http://example.com/{role}/{user}")]
      (example-parser "http://example.com/admin/dfa")) ; yields {:role "admin"
      	  :user "user" }

